VYDBUr YHVH 'aL-MShH V'aL-'aHUrN L'aMUr.
Z'aTh ChQTh HThVUrH 'aShUr-TShVH YHVH L'aMUr DBUr 'aL-BNY YShUr'aL VYQChV 'aLYK PhUrH 'aDMH ThMYMH 'aShUr 'aYN-BH MVM 'aShUr L'a-'yLH 'yLYH 'yL.
VNThThM 'aThH 'aL-'aL'yZUr HKHN VHVTShY'a 'aThH 'aL-MChVTSh LMChNH VShChT 'aThH LPhNYV.
VLQCh 'aL'yZUr HKHN MDMH B'aTShB'yV VHZH 'aL-NKCh PhNY 'aHL-MV'yD MDMH ShB'y Ph'yMYM.
VShUrPh 'aTh-HPhUrH L'yYNYV 'aTh-'yUrH V'aTh-BShUrH V'aTh-DMH 'yL-PhUrShH YShUrPh.
VLQCh HKHN 'yTSh 'aUrZ V'aZVB VShNY ThVL'yTh VHShLYK 'aL-ThVK ShUrPhTh HPhUrH.
VKBS BGDYV HKHN VUrChTSh BShUrV BMYM V'aChUr YB'a 'aL-HMChNH VTM'a HKHN 'yD- H'yUrB.
VHShUrPh 'aThH YKBS BGDYV BMYM VUrChTSh BShUrV BMYM VTM'a 'yD-H'yUrB.
V'aSPh 'aYSh THVUr 'aTh 'aPhUr HPhUrH VHNYCh MChVTSh LMChNH BMQVM THVUr VHYThH L'yDTh BNY-YShUr'aL LMShMUrTh LMY NDH ChT'aTh HV'a.
VKBS H'aSPh 'aTh-'aPhUr HPhUrH 'aTh-BGDYV VTM'a 'yD-H'yUrB VHYThH LBNY YShUr'aL VLGUr HGUr BThVKM LChQTh 'yVLM.
HNG'y BMTh LKL-NPhSh 'aDM VTM'a ShB'yTh YMYM.
HV'a YThChT'a-BV BYVM HShLYShY VBYVM HShBY'yY YTHUr V'aM-L'a YThChT'a BYVM HShLYShY VBYVM HShBY'yY L'a YTHUr.
KL-HNG'y BMTh BNPhSh H'aDM 'aShUr-YMVTh VL'a YThChT'a 'aTh-MShKN YHVH TM'a VNKUrThH HNPhSh HHV'a MYShUr'aL KY MY NDH L'a-ZUrQ 'yLYV TM'a YHYH 'yVD TM'aThV BV.
Z'aTh HThVUrH 'aDM KY-YMVTh B'aHL KL-HB'a 'aL-H'aHL VKL-'aShUr B'aHL YTM'a ShB'yTh YMYM.
VKL KLY PhThVCh 'aShUr 'aYN-TShMYD PhThYL 'yLYV TM'a HV'a.
VKL 'aShUr-YG'y 'yL-PhNY HShDH BChLL-ChUrB 'aV BMTh 'aV-B'yTShM 'aDM 'aV BQBUr YTM'a ShB'yTh YMYM.
VLQChV LTM'a M'yPhUr ShUrPhTh HChT'aTh VNThN 'yLYV MYM ChYYM 'aL-KLY.
VLQCh 'aZVB VTBL BMYM 'aYSh THVUr VHZH 'yL-H'aHL V'yL-KL-HKLYM V'yL- HNPhShVTh 'aShUr HYV-ShM V'yL-HNG'y B'yTShM 'aV BChLL 'aV BMTh 'aV BQBUr.
VHZH HTHUr 'yL-HTM'a BYVM HShLYShY VBYVM HShBY'yY VChT'aV BYVM HShBY'yY VKBS BGDYV VUrChTSh BMYM VTHUr B'yUrB.
V'aYSh 'aShUr-YTM'a VL'a YThChT'a VNKUrThH HNPhSh HHV'a MThVK HQHL KY 'aTh- MQDSh YHVH TM'a MY NDH L'a-ZUrQ 'yLYV TM'a HV'a.
VHYThH LHM LChQTh 'yVLM VMZH MY-HNDH YKBS BGDYV VHNG'y BMY HNDH YTM'a 'yD-H'yUrB.
VKL 'aShUr-YG'y-BV HTM'a YTM'a VHNPhSh HNG'yTh ThTM'a 'yD-H'yUrB.
